16:T54b,Tracy is soul guide and mentor, energetic interpreter, and international facilitator based on the Kohala Coast. She is given to empowering souls deeply landed in matter and honoring the multitude of realities and expressions of love within each of us. Tracy has spent the last decade immersed in both study and practice within traditions of healing and integration, energetic mastery, and soul initiation. She combines lived experience, years of training and depth of study with intuitive adeptness and precise energetic attunement in her work. 

Tracy's soul mentorship is focused on midwifing souls into embodied depth and well being.  Her one on one practice welcomes individuals and couples and covers the following:
-Emotional fluency
-Nervous system regulation and stabilization
-Neuroplasticity training
-Relational wellness
-Erotic embodiment
-Practical integration for soulful living
-Clearing patterns and behaviors that inhibit wellness and radiance

Tracy's group work focuses on supporting fields of vibratory coherence between humans and building group capacity for generative healing , creativity, and collaboration. This work is deeply supportive for organizations, collectives, and any group wanting to understand relational dynamics to support generative and resourcing environments. Reach out directly to find out more about group work.17:T5a1,Support for:  Emotional/Relational Trauma, Burn-out, Stress & Anxiety, Grief & Loss, Family Conflicts, Life Transitions & Addictions
Approach: Trauma-Informed, Strength-based, Family Systems & Outcomes-focus

Aloha, I am a Hawaii and California licensed MFT and Certified Substance Abuse Counselor offering professional counseling and life coaching services to adults, adolescence, couples, and families in-person at Kailua-Kona, or telehealth to all other communities statewide.

As a bi-cultural engineer-turned-therapist with senior leadership background, I am experience in various clinical specialties that enables me to provide effective, high impact, outcome-focused services to my clients. 

I welcome opportunities in supporting adults, young adults, couples & families to navigate through tough seasons of feeling overwhelmed, experiencing loss in transitions, or dealing with painful/complex circumstances, whiles having a sensitivity to generational, cultural, & racial influences.   

I tend to be a fit for those who are in technology, medical, legal, education, and any other industries with a relatively high intensity & high stress life-styles.   

My style is both conversational & experiential, with a high value on respect and safety, while advocating for empowerment & hope.

Book a free discovery today @  https://calendly.com/pursuewholeness/free15min, or
